action_description:
Ensure projects can be completed and products launched within defined deadlines by address-ing the root causes:
•	Before mandating new projects requiring R&D resources, ensure the consequences on ex-isting R&D tasks and projects are clarified and accepted. I.e., any new credit applications for R&D projects should specify the consequences/opportunity cost on existing projects;
•	Reduce priority changes that lead to delays on strategic projects. Any such changes shall be approved upfront by the DMM as required by the GFMS DoA;
•	Calculate the total resource needed in the software team to cover tasks from all other teams in addition to existing strategic projects. Based on this result, evaluate whether additional resources need to be procured or recruited.

Make use of the equipment failure summary automatically recorded in the Anton system and perform monthly failure analysis to identify and follow up on at least: frequently occurred failures, escalated failures (Anton will escalate equipment failures automatically if not solved within target time) and machines with the highest failure rates;
Make a clear definition of "machines with OEE constantly being below threshold", e.g. below the threshold for three consecutive months (the OEE threshold can be different for different types/importance levels of equipment). Perform root cause analysis and define action plans for such equipment and make sure they are documented and tracked till completion;
Keep an overview of maintenance plans and track the data with both e-copy and hard copy, make sure the execution of equipment maintenance is performed according to the plan, reconcile regularly to avoid any omissions.
利用安灯系统自动记录的设备故障汇总表，每月进行故障分析，至少要识别和跟踪：经常发生的故障、升级的故障（如果在目标时间内没有解决，安灯会自动升级设备故障）和故障率最高的机器。
对 "OEE持续低于阈值的机器 "做出明确定义，例如连续三个月低于阈值（不同类型/重要程度的设备，OEE阈值可以不同）。对这些设备进行根本原因分析并确定行动计划，确保这些计划被记录下来并跟踪到完成。
对维修计划和计划跟踪进行概述，包括电子版和纸质版，确保设备维修的执行是按照计划进行的，定期进行核对，以避免任何疏忽。

Develop a standard template of external warehouse rental service, and the following areas are recommended to be covered and streamlined in the template:
1. Responsibility between Chinaust Shanghai Auto and external warehouse suppliers in case of stock loss or damage;
2. Confidentiality terms regarding the information and documentation generated and exchanged during the cooperation;
3. Monthly bill structure and reconciliation methodology;
4. Monthly physical stock count arrangement and required reports.
制定一个驻外仓库租赁服务的标准模板，建议在模板中涵盖和统一以下方面：
1. 在库存损失或损坏的情况下，上海亚大和外部仓库供应商之间的责任划分; 
2. 合作期间产生和交换的信息和文件的保密条款；
3. 月度账单的构成和核对方法；
4. 每月的实物库存清点安排和所需报告。

