As discussed with the Purchasing Manager, the following operations are now in place:
- In case of new delivery dates mutually agreed, Purchasing employee need to change the SAP PO delivery date as soon as the date is confirmed.;
- For actual delays made solely by the Vendor, no SAP change will be made, and rational for the delays should be remarked in the monthly "Overdue PO Report";
- For potential manual errors or delays in changing the mutually agreed delivery date in SAP, Purchasing employees will make changes at month-end in SAP, but such cases should be limited and rationale should be given.
